          "name": "Leader",
          "type": "Abilities",
          "lines": [
            {
              "name": "Description",
              "value": "This model can be attached to the following units:\n\n■ Assault Intercessor Squad\n■ Bladeguard Veteran Squad\n■ Intercessor Squad\n■ Sternguard Veteran Squad\n■ Tactical Squad\n■ Company Heroes"
